The volume of the formula_54-dimensional body defined by formula_55, is bounded by the volume of the hypercube of size formula_56, hence formula_57. The hard part is to show that this bound still works on the average, i.e.,
Lemma. (&quot;Linnik&quot;) For all formula_58 there exists formula_59 and a constant formula_60, depending only on formula_32, such that for all formula_62,
